      h1 LFUCG Data
      p Data enpoints for integration with LFUCG vendors. Base URL is https://lfucg-data.herokuapp.com.
      h2 /api/v1/police
      p Returns police cases that occured on or after a supplied date.
      h3 Request Headers
      p API-KEY | string | Valid API Key string supplied by LFUCG
      h3 Query Parameters
      p lastupdated | date | ex. 05-15-2017
      h3 Example
      p
        | Return police cases on or after May 11, 2017.
      p https://lfucg-data.herokuapp.com/api/v1/police?lastupdated=05-11-2017

